    <abstract id="aspace_f3316bd350106331b47c4c2f4bedd2c2">This collection contains documents once in the possession of John McManigal, president of United Steelworkers of America Local 1397, 1964-1970. Included are minute books, union contracts and pension agreements, the Local 1397 newspaper The Sentinel, union election materials, and other documents.</abstract>
